summary: 2K Re-Texture of the floor, walls and roof on Sky Haven Temple!
descriptionHtml: This is the only hd re-texture of skyhaven temple, except from the hd re-texture of alduins wall by hellstorm102, which i highly recommend using with this mod. This is my first mod/retexture ever, but the textures are optimized. This is just a simple retexture, and i am not updating it or anything, and you can use it for your own mods, if you want. P.S. sorry for my bad english, not my main language.
author: MadzMaster
